CatDescriptText: Cutline of related article published in Pittsburgh Courier, November 5, 1955, pg. 14B reads: "African Premier Visits City - The Hon. Nnamdi Azikiwe, Prime Minister of Eastern Nigeria, West Africa, was in city, the guest of The Courier, Thursday, to advance plans for the establishment of the University of Nigeria...From The Courier, he went to Mellon Institute for a look-see at new scientific marvels on the boards..."
TitMainTitle: Eastern Nigerian Prime Minister Nnamdi Azikiwe wearing light colored agbada and dark cap, walking up steps toward columns of Mellon Institute, Oakland
